     DESCRIPTION:

    Need for Speed: Most Wanted - crazy race through a huge open city full of street racers as well as police officers. In this new Autolog allows you to easily track all activities (races, jumping on trampolines, passages at tremendous speeds past the cameras, etc.) of your friends and compare them with their achievements. 
Multiplayer redesigned so that, for the start of competition do not need to go on Standby screens and wait for arrival by looking at the table of participants. It's fairly easy to come to the place of the race, and after crossing the finish line you can turn around and try to ram the laggards.
